Designed to Withstand the Rigors of Life at Sea


We make electrical products that stand up to the harshest environments. Every product we make, from our rugged shore power cordsets and adapters to a wide array of 12V accessories, is designed to withstand the rigors of life at sea. 
We engineer our products to exacting performance specifications, including CSA and MARINE UL listings for an extra margin of safety. And as the world’s leading manufacturer of shore power accessories, we offer a complete line of products to meet practically every application – wherever your port of call.















 



