NEWS



Marinco 70A Trolling Motor Plug Wins Industry Award
As a global leader in Marine Electrical Equipment, Marinco is honoured that the new 70A trolling motor plug and receptacle has recently been named one of the top 50 products of 2017 by Boating Industry.


Read the full press release



Power Products LLC acquires FL based Lenco Marine
Lenco Marine is a recognized leader in innovation, product quality, and customer service in the marine industry since its founding in 1986.


Read the full press release



Mastervolt System Provides Performance for the Volvo Ocean Race Vessels
Mastervolt was chosen as the official electrical supplier to the Volvo Ocean Race because of its integrated, technologically advanced systems and rugged components that can handle the abusive conditions of this around the world race.


Read full press release



Power Products, LLC Acquires Blue Sea Systems® on October 31, 2014
Blue Sea Systems is a recognized leader in the design and manufacture of products for marine and specialty vehicle electrical systems, including circuit protection, battery switches, busbars, power distribution panels, and battery chargers.


Read full press release















